It's not a solution to climate change and it might even be a welcome excuse for the fossil fuel industry to delay the end of the fossil fuel age.

76
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:11,020
Over the last few decades, geoengineering has been so controversial that it stopped many scientists from doing the experiments necessary to understand it better.

77
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:15,020
But blankly opposing geoengineering is short-sighted.

78
